{"title":"古山寨（外一首）","authors":["唐德亮"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"古山寨（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐德亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千年古寨不老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过纤细的血管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山风砍伐着一茬又一茬的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又长出一个个杉皮树般的黑色山民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是其中一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千年前捧着月亮喝酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千年后踩着彩虹飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采撷鸟儿的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破译山鬼的偈语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月已长出皱纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我的心却长出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨露与花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚桃果砸额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚桃果逃离树枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸在他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夹皮沟一样的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的桃果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明的皮肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的目光之外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的阴影之内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向他绽露甜甜的笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疼痛的感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时被这欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸得无影无踪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满树的鲜桃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵粉霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱着另一朵粉霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让这霞光统统砸在身上吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想。那该是什么滋味呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚鲜桃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸在额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"额头上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长出一片云霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒野说：这是历史深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动人的一簇亮点"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}